==Translingual==

===Pronunciation===
/ r /, often transliterated as r. Pronounced alone it is / rə / similar to the beginning of the English word [[run]].

===Letter===
'''र''' (r)

#The second [[semivowel]] of the [[Devanagari]] script, but traditionally classified (and [[collated]]) as a consonant. Linguistically it is considered an alveolar trill, and is classified as an [[approximant]].


